#

Berry Yogurt Parfait

10 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts (if granola contains nuts)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanHealthy

Course:

BreakfastSnack

Tags:

QuickHealthyNo-CookBreakfastSnack

Description

A refreshing and healthy layered treat with creamy yogurt, fresh berries, and crunchy granola.

Ingredients

  • greek yogurt: 2 cups
  • mixed berries (strawberries, blueberries, raspberries): 1 cup
  • granola: 1 cup
  • honey (optional): 2 tablespoons
